<h2 id="usage"><a href="#usage">Usage</a></h2>

<section class="prose">
  <p>Input groups are achieved through composition using relative positioning and Tailwind utilities. No special component needed - just wrap your input with a positioned container and add your icons, text, or buttons.</p>
  <p><strong>Key patterns:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Use <code>relative</code> wrapper around input</li>
    <li>Position content with <code>absolute</code> + <code>top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2</code></li>
    <li>Add padding to input (<code>pl-*</code> or <code>pr-*</code>) to make room for content</li>
    <li>Use <code>pointer-events-none</code> for decorative icons</li>
  </ul>
</section>

