<h2 id="accessibility"><a href="#accessibility">Accessibility</a></h2>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li>Use <code>pointer-events-none</code> for decorative icons that shouldn't be interactive</li>
    <li>Ensure buttons have proper <code>aria-label</code> or visible text</li>
    <li>Maintain sufficient padding so text doesn't overlap with icons/buttons</li>
    <li>Use semantic button types (<code>type="button"</code> vs <code>type="submit"</code>)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

